# AI Dev Platform тАФ Codebase Review

## Overview

An enterprise-grade **AI-driven software development lifecycle platform**. Senior developers prompt AI agents, which generate, test, deploy, and monitor applications. The current state is a **fully functional frontend with mock data** тАФ no real backend yet. The codebase is clean, modular, and ready for API integration.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Library / Tool |
|---|---|
| Framework | React 19 + Vite 7 |
| Language | TypeScript (strict) |
| Routing | React Router DOM v7 |
| State/Fetching | TanStack Query v5 |
| UI Components | Radix UI (Shadcn-style pattern) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v3 + tailwind-animate |
| HTTP Client | Axios (configured, unused тАФ mock only) |
| Validation | Zod v4 |
| Icons | Lucide React |
| Charts | Recharts |
| IDs | UUID |
| Path Alias | `@/` тЖТ `src/`, `@/../mock/` тЖТ `mock/` |

