## Data Flow Pattern (Universal)

Every feature module follows the same data layer pattern:

```
mock/core/<module>/<Entity>Data.ts   тЖТ  TypeScript types + static data arrays
        тЖУ imported by
src/modules/<module>/hooks/use-<module>-data.ts   тЖТ  useQuery() wrapping mock with 500ms delay
        тЖУ consumed by
src/modules/<module>/pages/<module>-page.tsx      тЖТ  Page component
        тЖУ uses
src/modules/<module>/components/<component>.tsx   тЖТ  Pure display components
```

This pattern makes **swapping mock for real API calls trivial** тАФ only the [queryFn](file:///d:/PROJECTS/ai-dev-platform/src/modules/dashboard/hooks/use-dashboard-data.ts#9-21) bodies in hooks need updating.

