## Services Layer

### [axios-client.ts](file:///d:/PROJECTS/ai-dev-platform/src/services/api/axios-client.ts)
- `baseURL`: `VITE_API_BASE_URL` env var OR `http://localhost:5174`
- Auth: reads `token` from `localStorage` тЖТ sets `Authorization: Bearer <token>`
- 401 response interceptor present (handler is a stub тАФ no redirect yet)
- **All hooks currently bypass this client** (they import from mock directly)

### [query-provider.tsx](file:///d:/PROJECTS/ai-dev-platform/src/app/providers/query-provider.tsx)
- `retry: 1`
- `refetchOnWindowFocus: false`
- No staleTime set (defaults to 0 тАФ will refetch on every mount)

